Items.Title: Resolution calling on the New York State Legislature to pass, and the Governor to sign, A.2705/S.4801, relating to the amount of state aid reimbursement for public health services by a municipality in the city of New York when the municipality is providing some or all of certain identified core public health services.
Items.MatterName: Amount of state aid reimbursement for public health services by a municipality in the city of New York when the municipality is providing some or all of certain identified core public health services (A.2705/S.4801).
